*knetworkmanager-0.2.1_p20071228 (17 Feb 2008)

  17 Feb 2008; Robert Buchholz <rbu@gentoo.org>
  +files/knetworkmanager-0.2.1-autostart.patch,
  +knetworkmanager-0.2.1_p20071228.ebuild:
  Bump to newer svn snapshot to fix icon display. Additionally,
   - Depend on straight KDE 3.5 components (bug #206528)
   - Install proper autostart entry

  31 Dec 2007; Joseph Jezak <josejx@gentoo.org>
  knetworkmanager-0.2.1_pre20071119.ebuild:
  Marked ~ppc for bug #197237.

